name: 25,000 (FIFA 14 Ultimate Team Coins)
description: FIFA Ultimate Team is the incredible extension to your FIFA experience allowing you to build your dream team from over 8,000 FIFA players then compete in exciting tournaments & competitions against your friends or other skilled opponents in the massive online community. FIFA coins are the currency you need to bid on your star players, negotiate trade deals, purchase contracts, kits, stadiums or even packs for your chance at rare superstars like Rooney, Ronaldo or Messi! Give your club the perfect boost and save yourself valuable time by purchasing as many coins you need instantly. To receive your coins you must list on auction any unwanted player with a "Buy it Now" price equal to the total number of coins purchased. Provide your player’s details along with your Ultimate Team name when asked during checkout and we will buy your player as soon as possible*. For more information please check our FAQ’s page. *Please note the following... FIFA Ultimate team charge a 5% fee to sell players and items on auction known as EA tax. We DO NOT cover this EA tax charge . All content on EA’s servers including FIFA coins, remain the property of EA. By ordering with us you are paying Infinity Coins for the service of earning and delivering coins to you, along with any assistance required throughout that process.
